DARKNESS
INDOOR_FLOOR
NAME New Everhome
*DESCRIPTION_START
This house is a nice blend of nature and man. Many items here represent
than one race. Before you, a massive statue of a dragon sits on the
wall-to-wall rug. In front of the statue is a desk while portraits line
the walls
*DESCRIPTION_END
