This is a portrait of Drizzt Do'Urden, a highlander of great strength and
high determination. His lavender eyes blaze with an inner fire and rage.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 5 1308
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 5
Upon this portrait is a young aelfen who is usually known for his kindness
and ready smile, but on this occasion his face is twisted into a fearsome
visage. He is Sturm Brightblade, a mage of known power and varied skill.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 6 1308
